Shells

FISH
Finally, a command line shell for the 90s
https://github.com/fish-shell/fish-shell/?tab=readme-ov-file#packages-for-linux
sudo apt-add-repository ppa:fish-shell/release-4
sudo apt install fish
fish

To change default shell to fish:
https://fishshell.com/docs/current/#default-shell
echo /usr/local/bin/fish | sudo tee -a /etc/shells
chsh -s /bin/bash

BASH
Bourne Again Shell
The default shell on Debian-based distributions
